<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/44580097-elliot-j">Elliot J.</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">It is the last one he wrote before his death. Subsequent ones are written by other authors and the published as &quot;Robert Ludlum&apos;s xxxxxx by yyyyyy&quot;<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">It is the last one he wrote before his death. Subsequent ones are written by other authors and the published as "Robert Ludlum's xxxxxx by yyyyyy"<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
