              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3923667-cari?shelf=investigative-thriller">investigative-thriller</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1725752425" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5185605466402199676">Lame. I am usually a Ludlum fan but thus was drudgery to get through. The characters bumble their way through, constantly walking into danger unprepared, getting tons of people killed because they didn&apos;t take reasonable precautions. They let bad guys constantly get the drop on them even tho one is supposed to be a highly trained operative. And for pity sake, a sawed-off shotgun cannot be referred to as a rifle. *eyeroll* Basic weapon knowledge 101.</span>
